  "text": "From 2 studies, maternal malaria was estimated to contribute to 3-8% of infant mortality. One study [CITATION_1] provided a much higher PAR estimate (30%) for infant mortality caused by maternal malaria infection, but this was an ecologic comparison between very different communities, and unmeasured contributions to infant mortality may have biased this estimate.",
